{"tid":474100,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[襟按占] 好姐妹為咗嫁個ibanker 放棄拍咗七年男友","createTime":"2017-11-20T00:18:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-20T06:44:44.000Z","uid":73231,"like":6,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"1dd90451d21ca9370edf255fabc573d389b1274a","tid":474100,"uid":73231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T00:18:48.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n早排一個中學無見好耐下既好姐妹無啦啦約番我出去食韓國嘢，仲好興奮咁話食咩飲咩都佢請。<br />\n咁我以為佢搵到好路數，就緊係滿心歡喜咁諗住祝福佢啦。<br />\n點知佢見面打完招呼第一句就話：我同我呀文（假名，佢男友）散左。<br />\n我聽完當堂呆左，佢地中學開始一齊，一直都相處得好好，呀文係我地個級出哂名又高大又靚仔，個陣大家不知幾羨慕我姐妹同到佢一齊。<br />\n重點對話大約如下：<br />\n<br />\n我問：吓，點解要分手？我地大家都以為你地會結婚。<br />\n<br />\n姐妹：我係上次個professional development event 到識到個ibanker，講嘢好有紋有路、又上進又叻，仲表示對我好有興趣。<br />\n<br />\n我：真係咁大吸引力？但係你識左佢唔係好耐咋喎，而且呀文又唔係唔好，份人又孝順，為咗個ibanker放棄個本港最後一個好仔值得咩？<br />\n<br />\n姐妹：再好食嘅食物食得多都厭啦係咪？而且我第一個拍拖嘅對象就係佢，我根本就唔知佢係咪最適合我嗰個。同埋ibanker個老豆就係某大行高層，對我前景好有幫助。咁做人總要力爭上游架？唔通要學班垃圾咁不思進取咩？<br />\n<br />\n我個晚同佢傾到過左凌晨，冇見佢兩年，估唔到佢變到咁樣，我講乜佢都當我on99港女咁仲要教番我點樣做人、點樣力爭上游 唔好成日禾X襟珍珠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 講番個呀文，佢連原因係乜都唔知就無啦啦被分手，仲要係block哂contact按門鈴唔開門個隻。依家日日見住佢放負文上FB<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲將佢玩咗咁多年嘅LOL帳號都畀埋人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 啲人唔知內情仲留言安慰佢話咁多年感情一定係一場誤會ng# 我依家一見到個絕世好仔放負能量文個心就好唔安樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但係結果好姐妹又好似無動於衷咁 仲叫我快啲搵返個幫到我事業嘅男人又叫我唔好同呀文講分手原因 亦都唔好同我男友講 因為佢同呀文好好朋友 我進退兩難都唔知點算好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2dd6920352f13565b961902c32ec0d11fe8ae03","tid":474100,"uid":39786,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T00:21:31.000Z","msg":"臭G"},{"pid":"5052f2820c31f76e4e940429e466fa3380272ed2","tid":474100,"uid":48426,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T00:24:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 算啦 識唔識簡人做女朋友都好重要"},{"pid":"fc42bf7a05aceb7287550f0a857b5da6f4909452","tid":474100,"uid":83420,"like":24,"dislike":3,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T00:25:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f669601ac87558436522ba89d7f359336c3759b3","tid":474100,"uid":97609,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T00:26:46.000Z","msg":"垃圾文"},{"pid":"f6f84eb69bb5d372200ecd8423ff76c44d9588f1","tid":474100,"uid":73231,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T00:26:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自己諗個新故事啦<br />\n抄到十足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但試到第一個回覆就係話 G<br />\n<br />\nI rest my point <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a23e626e2b4fdbcae520e550790bd5132d64526","tid":474100,"uid":130714,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T00:30:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>自己諗個新故事啦<br />\n抄到十足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但試到第一個回覆就係話 G<br />\n<br />\nI rest my point <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n連登洗試咩 依樣野係一早前設左啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8d0e26e48ec54407f9ff9954c1cac5eba9a64de","tid":474100,"uid":60169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T04:53:41.000Z","msg":"差緊啲激情位。建議重作"},{"pid":"c15b4b2279bb9c33ffcfd5167585613f2f588098","tid":474100,"uid":99048,"like":